workflow.description:
# CFO Forecasting Agent - Marketplace Listing

## Headlines (Choose Your Favorite)

### Option 1 - Direct & Professional
**"AI-Powered CFO Forecasting Agent: Automated Revenue Predictions from Stripe Data"**

### Option 2 - Benefit-Focused
**"Automate Your Financial Forecasting: Daily Revenue Predictions with AI Intelligence"**

### Option 3 - Action-Oriented
**"Transform Stripe Sales Data into Intelligent 3-Month Revenue Forecasts Automatically"**

---

## Marketplace Description

### üöÄ **AI-Powered Financial Forecasting on Autopilot**

Turn your Stripe sales data into intelligent revenue forecasts with this comprehensive CFO Forecasting Agent. This workflow automatically analyzes your transaction history, identifies trends, and generates professional 3-month revenue predictions using OpenAI's GPT-4.

### ‚ú® **What This Workflow Does:**

- **üìä Automated Data Collection**: Fetches and processes all Stripe charges daily
- **ü§ñ AI-Powered Analysis**: Uses OpenAI GPT-4 to analyze trends and predict future revenue
- **üìà Structured Forecasting**: Generates monthly forecasts with confidence levels and insights
- **üíæ Multi-Platform Storage**: Saves results to both Supabase database and Google Sheets
- **üïí Scheduled Execution**: Runs automatically every day to keep forecasts current
- **üß† Smart Context**: Optional Pinecone integration for historical context and improved accuracy

### üîß **Key Features:**

- **Daily automated execution** at 9 AM
- **Structured JSON output** with forecasts, trends, and confidence levels
- **Dual storage system** for data backup and easy reporting
- **RAG-enabled** for enhanced forecasting with historical context
- **Professional CFO-grade insights** and trend analysis

### üìã **Prerequisites:**

- Stripe account with API access
- OpenAI API key (GPT-4 recommended)
- Google Sheets API credentials
- Supabase account (optional)
- Pinecone account (optional, for enhanced context)

### üéØ **Perfect For:**

- SaaS companies tracking subscription revenue
- E-commerce businesses needing sales forecasts
- Startups requiring investor-ready financial projections
- Finance teams automating reporting workflows

### üì¶ **What You Get:**

- Complete n8n workflow with all nodes configured
- Detailed documentation and setup instructions
- Sample data structure and output formats
- Ready-to-use Google Sheets template

---

### üí° **Need Help or Want to Learn More?**

**Created by Yaron Been** - Automation & AI Specialist

- üìß **Support**: Yaron@nofluff.online
- üé• **YouTube Tutorials**: [https://www.youtube.com/@YaronBeen/videos](https://www.youtube.com/@YaronBeen/videos)
- üíº **LinkedIn**: [https://www.linkedin.com/in/yaronbeen/](https://www.linkedin.com/in/yaronbeen/)

*Get more automation tips, tutorials, and advanced workflows on my channels!*

---

### üè∑Ô∏è **Tags:** 
`AI`, `OpenAI`, `Stripe`, `Forecasting`, `Finance`, `CFO`, `Automation`, `Revenue`, `Analytics`, `GPT-4`

parameters.content:
## 1Ô∏è‚É£ **üîÅ Data Retrieval & Preprocessing**

**Nodes:**

* üïí `Run Daily Forecast`
* üü¶ `Fetch Stripe Charges`
* üß© `Summarize Daily Sales`
* ‚úèÔ∏è `Prepare Forecast Prompt`

---

### üïí `Run Daily Forecast`

**Type:** Cron Trigger
**Purpose:**
Automatically runs the workflow every day to keep forecasts updated with the latest sales data.

üîß **Configuration:**

* Schedule: Daily at 6 AM UTC (or as needed)

---

### üü¶ `Fetch Stripe Charges`

**Type:** Stripe Node
**Purpose:**
Retrieves all successful transactions from Stripe in a defined timeframe.

üì• **Details:**

* Resource: `Charges`
* Operation: `Get Many`
* Filters:

  * `created[gte]` (e.g. last 30 days)
  * `status: succeeded`
* Expansion (optional): `data.customer` for customer context

‚úÖ **Output:** Raw Stripe sales data with timestamps and amounts

---

### üß© `Summarize Daily Sales`

**Type:** Code Node
**Purpose:**
Processes Stripe charges and summarizes revenue per day.

üß† **Logic:**

* Converts Unix timestamps to `YYYY-MM-DD`
* Aggregates total revenue per day
* Converts cents to dollars

üì¶ **Output Sample:**

```json
{
  "2025-05-01": 1245.50,
  "2025-05-02": 980.00
}
```

---

### ‚úèÔ∏è `Prepare Forecast Prompt`

**Type:** Edit Fields / Function
**Purpose:**
Formats the summary into a natural language prompt for OpenAI.

üß† **Example Prompt:**

```txt
Given the following sales data:
{ "2025-05-01": 1245.50, ... }

Predict trends and forecast sales for the next 3 months.
```

üßæ **Output:** `prompt` (String) ‚Üí sent to the AI Agent

## 2Ô∏è‚É£ **ü§ñ AI Agent Forecasting**

**Nodes:**

* ü§ñ `Forecast with OpenAI Agent`
* üß† `OpenAI GPT-4 Model`
* üìÑ `Extract Forecast Output`
* üå≤ `Store Context in Pinecone` *(Optional)*
* üß¨ `Generate Embeddings` *(Optional)*

---

### ü§ñ `Forecast with OpenAI Agent`

**Type:** Tools Agent
**Purpose:**
Acts as an intelligent agent that reads the sales summary and responds with forecasts and reasoning.

üß† **Prompt Input:**
Passed from `Prepare Forecast Prompt`

üí¨ **Uses:**

* Model: `GPT-4`
* Output Parser: Structured JSON format

üìà **Forecast Intent:**
Predicts next 3 months, identifies trends, and gives a confidence level

---

### üß† `OpenAI GPT-4 Model`

**Type:** OpenAI Node
**Purpose:**
Handles the natural language generation based on the supplied prompt.

üßæ **Configuration:**

* Model: `gpt-4` or `gpt-4-turbo`
* Temperature: `0.2` (more deterministic)
* Max Tokens: `1000`

---

### üìÑ `Extract Forecast Output`

**Type:** Structured Output Parser
**Purpose:**
Parses the GPT response into usable JSON format.

üì¶ **Expected Output:**

```json
{
  "forecast": {
    "June": "$15,000.00",
    "July": "$16,500.00",
    "August": "$17,200.00"
  },
  "trend": "Increasing",
  "confidence": "High",
  "insights": "Sales show strong momentum..."
}
```

---

### üå≤ `Store Context in Pinecone` *(optional)*

**Type:** Vector Store
**Purpose:**
Indexes past data for retrieval-based prompting (RAG). Useful for long-term memory.

---

### üß¨ `Generate Embeddings` *(optional)*

**Type:** Embeddings Node
**Purpose:**
Converts text into vector format before inserting into Pinecone.

## 3Ô∏è‚É£ **üì¶ Storage & Reporting**

**Nodes:**

* üü© `Save Forecast to Supabase`
* üìä `Log Forecast in Google Sheets`

---

### üü© `Save Forecast to Supabase`

**Type:** Supabase Node
**Purpose:**
Stores all forecast results for analytics, versioning, or historical comparisons.

üõ¢Ô∏è **Table:** `forecasts`
üßæ **Columns Example:**

| timestamp  | raw\_data | forecast\_data |
| ---------- | --------- | -------------- |
| 2025-05-29 | {...}     | {...}          |

---

### üìä `Log Forecast in Google Sheets`

**Type:** Google Sheets Node
**Purpose:**
Pushes structured data into a visual format for reporting dashboards or human review.

üìã **Column Format:**

| Date       | Forecast (USD) | Trend      | Confidence | Insights                   |
| ---------- | -------------- | ---------- | ---------- | -------------------------- |
| 2025-05-29 | \$15,000.00    | Increasing | High       | Sales rising at 10% weekly |

---

## ‚úÖ Summary Flow

```txt
üîÅ Sales Data (Stripe) 
 ‚Üí üß† Forecast Agent (OpenAI) 
 ‚Üí üì¶ Stored in Supabase 
 ‚Üí üìä Reported in Google Sheets
